      <title>肖尔茨警告称，通胀反弹将危及欧洲央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/scholz-warns-of-jeopardizing-ecb-rate-cut-with-inflation-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨敦促保持克制，以避免新一轮通胀，从而阻止欧洲央行降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/scholz-warns-of-jeopardizing-ecb-rate-cut-with-inflation-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 18:01:13 GMT</pubDate>
