    <item>
      <title>国家银行首席执行官抨击加拿大增加资本利得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/national-bank-na-ceo-slams-canada-s-capital-gains-tax-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大最大银行之一的首席执行官公开反对特鲁多政府提高资本利得税的计划，认为这不会刺激该国的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/national-bank-na-ceo-slams-canada-s-capital-gains-tax-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 17:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
