    <item>
      <title>波兰将在 2025 年担任欧盟轮值主席国期间将国防作为首要任务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/poland-to-make-defense-top-priority-during-2025-eu-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长安杰伊·多曼斯基周五表示，波兰计划在一月份接任欧盟轮值主席国时加大力度推动增加国防开支。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/poland-to-make-defense-top-priority-during-2025-eu-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 17:17:25 GMT</pubDate>
